item.turbo:content:
<! [CDATA[
 Silicon Valley Bank Logo
Silicon Valley Bank, a subsidiary of SVB Financial Group, is a U.S.-based high-tech commercial bank. The bank has helped fund more than 30,000 start-ups. SVB is on the list of largest banks in the United States. It’s the biggest bank in Silicon Valley. The bank operates in different countries, e. g. India and Great Britain. The bank is also one of the largest providers of financial services to wine producers in Napa Valley.
You can download theSVBlogo on full-version of the page.
